@wp.kernel

    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = 0.71
    v1 = 0.71
    v0 = ((wp.abs(tmp + 0.17) * (tmp + 0.57 / v1 + 0.08)) - (wp.sin(v0 + 0.80) + v1))
    v1 = wp.exp(wp.exp(wp.exp(v2 + 0.28)))
